# Environment Variables for LoadSaathi

# Required Clerk variables
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your_clerk_publishable_key_here

# Required Supabase variables
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Optional Gemini API key (for AI search)
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key

# Add other environment variables as needed...

# NOTE: 
# 1. Replace the placeholder values with your actual keys from:
#    - Clerk Dashboard → API Keys (https://dashboard.clerk.com/last-active?path=api-keys)
#    - Supabase Project Settings → API
#    - Google Gemini API Console
# 2. Never commit real secrets to version control - keep this file in .gitignore
# 3. Create a .env file from this template for local development